Third-Party Licenses
====================

This file lists the third-party software packages used by the
nemo-rl container image and their respective licenses.

A complete, auto-generated Software Bill of Materials (SBOM) is
available inside the container at:

    /THIRD-PARTY-LICENSES   (per-package license text)
    /SBOM.txt               (CSV inventory)

To extract from a built image:

    docker run --rm nemo-rl-workshop cat /SBOM.txt > SBOM.txt


